For Emmet to be able to recognice .tmpl
I needed to add ctr+shift+p "Open User Settings (JSON)"
Then add:

"files.associations": {
    "*.tmpl": "html"
  }

=================================================================

To create a Go module. This app uses Go
Import third party packages
This app uses all the standard library and also uses external dependencies
$ go mod init myapp e.g (github.com/rodsilva/go-course)

===================================================================

Packages always lives under their own directories

====================================================================

How to run program?

go run cmd/web/*.go
or
go run ./cmd/web

====================================================================

Import from Github
go get -u github.com/go-chi/chi/v5

Clean unused modules from go.mod
go mod tidy


